We are grateful to Dr. Irina Dey for her excellent treatment as well as excellent surgical experience which she applied with our patient Mrs.Sahajadi Begam and returned her from a very serious condition to a healthy normal life within a very short period.Our heartiest blessings and dua for Dr.Irina Dey .We pray to God for Dr. Mam as if she can go miles after miles as a successful, efficient surgeon and in this way she can help lacks of serious patients to get back to their normal healthy life.We wish Dr.Irina Dey for her all success and all goodness for her family.

The overall experience was good, I have received good treatment as well as good medical care. I would certainly recommend my friends and relatives to visit the hospital and get treated under Dr Irina dey for gynaecology issues.

At first my wife was being monitored by another doctor till her first five months of pregnancy then, the first bump arrived and we had to change the doctor. We were in helpless then. Suddenly one of my colleague has advised me that I may visit Dr. Irina Dey. I was not sure, but the very first time we visited her, the way she has advised, taken away all our tension. We have followed her advice completely. 
However with the final scan on 33rd week, some complications were observed and that was the second bump. We were into mental trauma but again, Dr. Dey has taken more than half an hour to speak to us and helped us with all the necessary advice, which has boosted our experience. She gave best of the medicines and clarified all our doubts. In next 4 weeks, the complication has disappeared and I became a proud father of a healthy baby.

I would be always thankful to Dr. Dey for her extraordinary support.

*** ***** *** ** ******** *** **** ****** ** ***** **** *** for my wife's irregular menstruation problem. We were planning for a baby & Doc started the treatment in that direction. The journey of last 1 year (almost) was fabulous to say the least. The doc was too much caring & precautious in each & every step. She is confident, very friendly, has complete foresight of what she is doing & why she is doing. She communicates & explains each & everything to us. She would earn some extra brownie points for her protectiveness. She is so much caring that sometimes you feel like you are consulting your friend /relative who's also a doctor. That is very rare in today's time. We are blessed with a baby girl under her supervision at AMRI Dhakuria last week in these hard times of Covid pandemic. However, the consultation doesn't end here. She is doing the follow up checkups that would last for one more year. Let me tell you once again that, Doc. Dey is the best doctor you can consult. Meeting her was possibly the second best thing that happened to us (the birth of our child being the obvious first) during the pregnancy planning. I would recommend everyone to consult the Doc. Be rest assured you'd be in safe hands.

We went to Dr Irina Dey for diagnosis of Uterine Fibroids. Doctor was very good in diagnosing the issue and initially prescribed medication to resolve the issue without any surgery. But since the medication didn't resolved the issue properly, Doctor suggested for TAH+BSO surgery. The surgery was done by Doctor herself and it was done successfully without any complications. Doctor had been very supportive and cooperative with patient and family throughout the process, both pre and post operative care. A big thanks to Dr. Irina and AMRI hospital Dhakuria for the wonderful experience.

** ***** *** ** * *** ** ******* She is very friendly and experienced.  I am about to leave for studies in abroad in less than a month. In the meantime I was diagnosed with ovarian cyst and she suggested me for the immediate OT. I was very scared because of the post complications and about recovery duration but trust me after exactly 1 week of OT I'm writing this, here I am with very mild pain in my stomach and facing zero problems in walking and doing almost any activity.  It doesn't seem like I underwent a surgery few days back.  I am so happy with her overall treatment, even after post treatment the way she kept the record of my health is so overwhelming.  I would highly recommend her to anybody for any gynecological treatment.

Dr. Irina Dey is an excellent doctor. I felt confident enough to go through the surgery after being explained about the condition and the details of the surgical procedure by her. Post operative care was very good and the surgery wounds healed painlessly.
Post operative pain was minimal and the stitches healed very well. I am feeling blessed to have been treated by such a competent doctor. I would like to thank Doctor Irina Dey and AMRI Hospital for handling my case with such care and expertise.

survey_response.review_text: I was running through hectic work schedule during March 2018. Suddenly I fainted once at my office toilet and once at my house. Visited local doctor and she advised for haemoglobin test. Test result came 5.3 on 21st. Immediately late night my husband soumik admitted me at Dhakuria AMRI for blood transfusion. 22nd since morning ECG, X ray, Eco and late afternoon USG done. During USG it sorted that I am having tubunal pregnancy. Immediately Dr. Irina Dey came to USG room and came along with me to my hospital cabin. She was extremely worried and concerned more than me. She took immediate decision to operate me within an hour with blood back up. She managed to make understand Soumik about the emergency of the operation. After successful operation I was in ICU for 2 days. Everyone said I got my life back by God's grace. However to me Dr. Irina Dey is a representative of God. I didn't know her before. She is a very good and genuine doctor.

Very nice, ************* *** confident doctor. Went to her with the hope to cure my Dermoid cyst medical condition and the conversation I had withDr. Irina made me immediately decide for a laparoscopic removal. I got released the day after the surgery and was back to my feet within another couple of days…so far so good, I thank my doctor and recommend her very highly.
Doctor mam is very helpful. Doctor  mam is a good advisor.she  careful to me. She isa good  surgeon.

Well! To start with, we had an accident in 2017.
And then, we got a positive slide, and we were confused where to go as the last Doctor was a total mistake. Then we Googled, and found her. We read the reviews, and took a chance, A BIG chance with Dr. Irina Dey. And to our surprise, we were blessed to get a Doctor like her. Every step, every confusion, every anxiety, she worked like a God and we were sure after 2 visits that, we chose the right one. Today our Baby Girl is 21 days old, and I can bet my career that without her involvement, guidance and meticulous approach things would have gone awry. She not just guides her patients but takes double precaution and stress to ensure the mother and baby both are fine. During our pregnancy, she was always available, text, call and she’s there to respond. We were stressed at times, but her confidence of operating the issues were so calm that we had a blind faith on her and her prescriptions. We are blessed today, not just with our daughter but also because we had Dr. Irina Dey with us, all the way. She’s more like your friend, from whom you can always seek advice without hesitation.
We would rate her 15/10 if that’s possible. God has shown us the right path, and she was the medium.
I don’t know if there are far better doctors here in Kolkata, but she’s one you can always reach out to. Thumbs up & Kudos to her.

1 year ago I had visited Dr Irina Dey she diagnosed & motivated me & I have conceived naturally. I was very much frightened since my first pregnancy was not successful *** * **** ***** *** **** ****** and this time everything is going good.  Dr’s behaviour is so so good that I feel very happy and she diagnosed the issue deeply.  I highly recommend Dr Irina Dey for a beautiful pregnancy journey.
